description:
In this video, we're taking a look at one of my all-time favorite gospel songs  "Heaven Came Down" (key: E).
This song is powerful and uplifting, and I'm sure you'll love singing it along with me in this karaoke video!
If you're looking for a great way to express your love for God, then this hymn is perfect for you. 

Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters youtube channel.
